5. Manifest example

Base deployment:

# manifests-repo/apps/ui/base/deployment.yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: tasking-ui
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: tasking-ui
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: tasking-ui
    spec:
      containers:
        - name: tasking-ui
          image: registry.example.com/group/ui-repo/ui:placeholder
          ports:
            - containerPort: 8080
          readinessProbe:
            httpGet:
              path: /healthz
              port: 8080
          livenessProbe:
            httpGet:
              path: /healthz
              port: 8080

Base kustomization:

# manifests-repo/apps/ui/base/kustomization.yaml
resources:
  - deployment.yaml
  - service.yaml
  - ingress.yaml

Dev overlay:

# manifests-repo/apps/ui/overlays/dev/kustomization.yaml
resources:
  - ../../base
nameSuffix: -dev
images:
  - name: registry.example.com/group/ui-repo/ui
    newName: registry.example.com/group/ui-repo/ui
    digest: sha256:placeholder

Staging and prod-high would be the same pattern with environment-specific ingress, config, replica count, resource limits, etc.

